<div class="features">
    <h1>Still unsure? Here are more features.</h1>
    <h2>You would never believe how helpful this could be.</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Community</h3>
            <p>
               You can use other user's notes. 
               Other users can make notes, for
               you to read and study off of. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Categories</h3>
            <p>
               Categories can be used for finding notes that
               are too general to search for. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Search</h3>
            <p>
               You can search for other user's notes. 
               Convenient for when you don't have the notes
               or resources needed. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Intutive</h3>
            <p>
               Reguardless if you are on mobile or desktop,
               a clean and instinctive user interface leads you
               around.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Fast</h3>
            <p>
               Speed is key. NoteQuick tries to make the best
               experience possible by making sure there are no
               bottlenecks or bugs in our back-end code.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Everybody</h3>
            <p>
              <em>NoteQuick is not only for students and teachers.</em>
              NoteQuick is for anybody and <em>everybody</em> 
              who wants to share and make notes.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="clearer"></div>
        <div class="trybutton">Signup!</div>
    </div>
    <%= User.all.size %>
</div>
